  1. Changes in lobster size at MPA and non-MPA sites (comparing only 2012 and 2017 sizes)

From the data description (http://sbc.lternet.edu/cgi-bin/showDataset.cgi?docid=knb-lter-sbc.77):

At Isla Vista and Naples Reef, the two protected MPA sites (with zero fishing pressure), how do lobster sizes in 2012 and 2017 compare? At the non-MPA sites?

NOTE: In regards to number 3, MOHK, a non MPA site was the only site to show significant change from 2012 to 2017 and it was a decrease in mean carapace length. It doesnt look like fishing pressure significanlty affects carapace length
